---
const AIRBNB_URL = 'https://www.airbnb.com/h/n58?utm_source=website&utm_medium=about';
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-stone-50">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

      <div>
        <p class="text-timber text-xs font-medium tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">The Property</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl text-zinc-900 mb-6 leading-snug">
          Built for those who want to slow down.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          N58 sits at Nēģu 58 in Carnikava — a quiet village on the edge of the national park,
          where the Vecgauja river winds through the coastal pines before the Baltic Sea begins.
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          The house is new, modern, and designed around outdoor living. The motorised louvered
          pergola blurs the line between inside and out — open to the sun, tilted against the rain,
          or closed completely. The garden is large and private. The river is a two-minute walk.
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Riga is 30 km away. But once you're here, you probably won't want to leave.
        </p>
        <a
          href={AIRBNB_URL}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-block bg-charcoal hover:bg-zinc-700 text-white font-medium px-8 py-4 rounded-full transition-colors text-sm tracking-wide"
        >
          Check availability
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Replace about.jpg with a good interior or garden shot -->
        <div class="aspect-[3/4] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-zinc-200">
          <img
            src="/images/about.jpg"
            alt="N58 terrace and garden, Carnikava Latvia"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
            onerror="this.style.display='none'"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Stats card -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-5">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="font-display text-3xl text-timber font-medium">2</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-zinc-400 mt-1">Bedrooms</div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-px h-10 bg-zinc-100"></div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="font-display text-3xl text-timber font-medium">4</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-zinc-400 mt-1">Guests</div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-px h-10 bg-zinc-100"></div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="font-display text-3xl text-timber font-medium">1</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-zinc-400 mt-1">Bathroom</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
